author: @starhoshibyul
text:
I've been here since Sixteen days, since Day 1 of Twice & I'm so proud at what they achieved over the years. But you know, the one thing that I took pride about Twice is NOT their achievements & titles, but how after all these years, Twice still, always, always ALWAYS perform just like they are in their rookie daysâ€“ but with less nervousness + more confident with all the experience they have build up all these years.

The way they show their love to their fans are still the same as back then tooâ€“it's real, you know their heart is really in this, they ALL genuinely love what they're doing as idols TOGETHER, with each others & Onces despite everything (& not many idols/groups can say that sadly) even now, the light im their heart & eyes still shine so bright like their very first day, & honestly even brighter, so.

Even if I can't really catch up with their contents on time like before, or care much about streaming/voting, like I did back then due to life, I'm still here, watching their contents & listening their music at my own pace, buying albums & such, to support them however I can because I literally owe them my life, & I genuinely like them a lot too, they never gives me any reasons to leave, but instead they make me wanna stay here forever the more I see them so :))
